ntext determines the boundaries of a model, and a bounded context logically has one or more than one model.</p>\n<p>Bounded contexts can be distinguished based on the language used by domain members. With respect to the terms 'product' and 'member' of the shopping mall, the order/payment domain and the delivery domain each have different meanings, so the two domains are separated into different contexts.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1154 784' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-91666d38bd0a6880d761e217d3d7cab7'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-91666d38bd0a6880d761e217d3d7cab7)' width='1154' height='784' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%%2b/8aCkxMobOnbfAjvk/l8t3/QWx1F9LJwpGP4XA8rGWjl9PEgCEQurjeBZTbDAa4daLbqBFl4/BnY6CiSWx9ppFk4/D549D0BKhe/OAJkCzxkG4Pzbi15n6AZAidfkbHVdd73xnKHztcfza1PP05wu7DSnTTzFaabaWPU4llWPZLFqoM6i9VLb9H00Vl0fI27wtlo00pqaKllqalL0gQNl8guX2N4s3%%2b5hX1Pb9qWDRgoel6dMflmZMe7g9Y4qVrpVrDSflHKvyr9i5bciChbOiN27ODS6vKBi6e9e2wQcObB%2b4LX/NCNpcK%2bdwgwyjejnGDXKE6nxoRtEHzr4QMpFg%2bELY9cHuhEl0cwHSNcbbBUrCIrXb/SPANRNppJQKTI1nI6sfUGy2JFWqqZEFOnu4mj2y%2bIlj%2baS7hpXTH5atSDlftXPotapto%2b9vz0xo1hwMpCw6P5ZtlNnoE777S/ICT5mOSL%2b%2bSHvZHUY/u13v13TRIjXajL5Gq97XzGv9AAR/RMAAIDBqkBEgMK6Xgw7zYNcj3WHgAE8QwAu6xBOIq4lnzjCOJC2KqekFSsk5VC8zYHXfrcypmdspNnUvo8um8a51d1Bm6B39srS/7J5d8Hjn0nmPS5bNflS6YrpA1cgpMN4Oxlex3OidlpaocmyPrGKYEBtzzB%2bhWnlz/d6BFxS7B59XVg5qVh8MhHX8AQTiDTKE4Fr0iHp/M1PTE3RJAYMnvqBjV4WClTX6AuozKKa2j0sJUSEe18qO4Sb/K/yniVfxutTL1OaJl41bQq6ZN4Td0mUmPqIXZH6pyQ%2b2qE8EILbBn0Iq%2bSW22quItiUWGiyJZQYu9lOqJfGY5VJvXqmUPSlclvqoNH3Gg9KM5CfFy2Y79Ef7Upzazw0AMR67PIJCNb1Ap/lgtLxzYuySQ2D1cZCMhpN4JK6Ikbgz/hxWyLU053VXyI74xpwXdsX4acgX5o3jibTQpUF3bOkzTjUfClRZOCmL6mQEgAvsMe8S2hq/Q4fDtzSeGVmLji2%2bbctMuGdYnvJo99I5