ins required from analysis to development of non-blocking, event-driven MSA-based systems.</p>\n<p>The existing use case or class diagramming method was a method of refining requirements through customer interviews and recognizing entity structures through detailed design, but event storming can be performed without any pre-trained knowledge and tools.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1370 439' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-7f600664f509cd995e99a80a5fabdae2'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-7f600664f509cd995e99a80a5fabdae2)' width='1370' height='439' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAVCAIAAAB5SH/NAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAI5ElEQVRIx81XW2wU1xne57xE4qWVEqlVogipKG6T8AIEEtQ0UhoimZuUAoVAGkhioEohSZU%2bRHmAtCSqi0tD4ypWI0OoKZQUGwImxuBi4/iy9tq7XnvvO7uzt5md3bnfZ/rNHGNsExBV%2b9Cj0fGZf45nv%2b///%2b//zwTcW8NxHHfesG17zoKFY9vu/%2bUIzL8BzlwuJwhCoVBgGEbX9Wq1WiwW8/k8HqqqmslkNE0jxFiWLZfLiqIYhnHX1xMXyKJbyrls0eUqLlOwFdkzcmWXLXmWOuvwVc%2bia56lxsDi8lVHle%2bXAE3TAIoZmKLRKMdxoAFwkiThtlar4RZGLEZGRrAgBCiKwlOQBIFF0VtMAIAyM95VzNpUQgNK71dTbhYWCqD1VNSyTFcS3HzSpRIwOuW8Rmduv%%2bzszMYDN5Zo%2b/Uyvy0JsM08SO6oXuXpmuqUHdSUTsZQeiQaUZm2iIRwP/VZFmQZU3XFVnGbqRzuViEQOFaOBK4EQcskP1gBUrIHzxCasHBJPFAEvvhBUiIqBmiGhwcBPrea9dA%2bK76vtM4Kx7LMA0b3rUt0o8cU3OZnMsVvXJMxevBQXpyUiqXA%2bLYmFEouABdqaQB2nUZTcuxLCdJpmUBK/yKWgToKFDAjZQAaPBBBEAAMQFicAMxEgF7XugRFl3TdMO0HMe0vcvwrlsbBM6rsKhRuCR%2bNlMUXRMUhZcwY61LmqkZmiAWR4Zn2v48%2bvFvr75z8J%2b7dp7auOnD73y373dHAj2BwPDSpeHGxrHGxsnXX48dOjR86FDhwgUxHkeCC6IIfMAEJkgkOBtMkGCILjgAMXAb/gBW0ECsCIFZEfuD14wYy8erQooTaUHJ8bJm%2bXvQB5DWKKZM0UhOESVILC%2bUapjFSl1iBbHMndn%2bymdr1/5927YTjetPbth4dueuc6/t/urAwa79v0x0XwmMPffcwMqVwWeeGVuxItjQMPLYY%%2bMajMzwT174sePz3R0xAcGkMtT4bAK5I6TKJU